@description.name: @description
@description.body: Classes which implement this interface are required to be disposed when they are no longer needed, by calling .dispose(); they are also registered with qx.core.ObjectRegistry so that qx.core.ObjectRegistry.fromHashCode() will work. Note that classes do not have to implement this interface in order to provide a dispose method and/or a destructor.
